headline: DARDEN RESTAURANTS, INC. ANNOUNCES NEW BOARD MEMBER
summary: Darden Restaurants, Inc. (NYSE: DRI) today announced the Board of Directors has appointed Daryl Kenningham as its newest member, effective immediately. With his appointment, the Company increased the size of the Board from nine to 10 members.
